:

*Zgrada* se trese. (The building is shaking.)
Čuje se buka iz *zgrade*. (Noise can be heard from the building.)
Gledala je *zgradu* od prozora. (She was looking at the building from the window.)
Nešto se događa u *zgradi*. (Something is happening in the building.)
U *zgradu* su se uputili u ranim jutarnjim satima. (They headed towards the building in the early morning hours.)